    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Public presentation of or calling attention to a product, service, event, or idea, that is openly paid for by an identified entity. Media for advertising include print and online publications, posters, television, and other media.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
